<!--zh
<magic_project_mechanism>
Magic Project 机制（类似 macOS .app）：

核心：文件夹内含 magic.project.js = 前端识别为 Magic Project

magic.project.js 操作约束：
- 格式为 JSONP（非 JSON），由专用工具生成
- 禁止用文件工具直接创建
- 允许用编辑工具修改其中的参数

前端如何区分渲染：
- 普通文件夹：显示📁图标，点击即展开文件夹看文件列表
- Magic Project：显示项目图标（如🎵），点击即打开专属面板（加载 index.html 可视化界面）

用户操作：
- 点击项目图标：打开项目面板（不是进入文件夹，也不是打开 index.html 文件）
- 点击项目名旁的小箭头：展开看里面的原始文件（类似展开普通文件夹）

项目类型：type 可选 audio、slide 等，整个文件夹被称作"超级产物"
</magic_project_mechanism>
-->
<magic_project_mechanism>
Magic Project Mechanism (similar to macOS .app):

Core: Folder containing magic.project.js = Frontend recognizes as Magic Project

magic.project.js operation constraints:
- Format is JSONP (not JSON), generated by dedicated tools (e.g., setup_audio_project)
- Never create directly using write_file or other file tools
- Allowed to modify parameters inside using edit_file (e.g., metadata.speakers)

Frontend rendering differentiation:
- Regular folder: Shows 📁 icon, click to expand folder and view file list
- Magic Project: Shows project icon (e.g., 🎵), click to open dedicated panel (loads index.html visualization interface)

User operations:
- Click project icon: Open project panel (not entering folder, not opening index.html file)
- Click arrow next to project name: Expand to see internal raw files (like expanding regular folder)

Project types: type options include audio, slide, etc. Entire folder called "super deliverable"
</magic_project_mechanism>
